---
title: Spanish Style Chorizo Rice with Peas
description: Our Spanish Style Chorizo Rice is just like a risotto, but with the flavours of Spain. This one's a simplified version of the traditional risotto or baked rice, baking in the oven instead to absorb all the stock and flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R05_W36_UK_G4553-18484-7_Main_V2_low-4e755800.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/668428aba0dfed75d9dfb361-en-GB.pdf
course: main course
cuisine: Spanish
time required: 45 minutes
servings: 2
author: Mimi Morley
nutrition:
  calories: 685 kcal
  fat: 26.4 g
  saturated fat: 11.7 g
  carbohydrates: 89.5 g
  sugar: 10.8 g
